  "description": "This dataset comprises intracranial EEG recordings from 121 individuals performing an auditory-naming task. Electrode coordinates are provided in MNI-305 stereotactic space. The dataset includes event markers for stimulus onset, stimulus offset, and response onset, enabling analysis of neural dynamics during speech production and auditory processing.",
  "methods_description": "Intracranial EEG recordings were acquired during an auditory-naming task. Event codes mark stimulus onset (401), stimulus offset (402), and response onset (501). Electrode coordinates are registered to MNI-305 space.",
